&lt;h2 id="css-tricks">Css-Tricks&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>There is a lot of css options for class, use it like bootstrapp :&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>options class=&amp;quot;&amp;quot; :
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>text-justify&lt;/li>
&lt;li>text-center&lt;/li>
&lt;li>no-deco =&amp;ldquo;text-decoration:none&amp;rdquo;&lt;/li>
&lt;li>float-left&lt;/li>
&lt;li>float-right&lt;/li>
&lt;li>a =&amp;ldquo;cursor: pointer&amp;rdquo;&lt;/li>
&lt;li>justify-between&lt;/li>
&lt;li>flex&lt;/li>
&lt;li>flex-even&lt;/li>
&lt;li>flex-wrap&lt;/li>
&lt;li>no-list&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>Check the css page :&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>\assets\css\default.css&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h2 id="share-options">Share-Options&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>List of :&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>facebook&lt;/li>
&lt;li>linkedin&lt;/li>
&lt;li>reddit&lt;/li>
&lt;li>telegram&lt;/li>
&lt;li>twitter&lt;/li>
&lt;li>whatsapp&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>Be carefull, the navbarShare is not in hidemeta for all posts or page who use /_default/single.html&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>You can add it if you want.&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>If you don&amp;rsquo;t want to see the sharebar in list, like homepage, yoursite.com/posts/, yoursite.com/tags(categories / series)/nameoftags/.&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Delete navbarshare in /_default/list.html&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h2 id="cover-image">Cover-Image&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>You can add a cover image to your post like this &lt;a class="sources-link" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="https://subversive-eu.github.io/hugo-subversive/posts/example/" >one&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>About installating check &lt;a class="sources-link" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="https://subversive-eu.github.io/hugo-subversive/posts/install/#more-options" >here&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
